Finance Agreement :PA Annex to Schedule - 9 a-c and 11 a-i | Description :Water supply companies to prepare and provide annualfinancial statements; produce total revenues equivalent to agreed amount; and maintain a debt service coverage ratio of not lessthan 1.3. | Frequency :Yearly

Finance Agreement :PA Annex to Schedule -10 a-c and 11 a-ii | Description :Borrowing and asset operating entities to prepare andprovide annual financial statements; to produce total revenues equivalent to agreed amount and maintain an agreed debt servicecoverage ratio. | Frequency :Yearly

Finance Agreement :PA Schedule Section IV | Description :Design a non-revenue water reduction (NRW) strategy by September 30, 2010;implement NRW reduction in three towns as a pilot, and thereafter complete implementation in six additional towns. By Januar | DueDate :30-Sep-2010
